data.title: The Fillmore Miami Beach at Jackie Gleason Theater
data.meta_description: The Fillmore Miami Beach at Jackie Gleason Theater tickets and upcoming 2024 event schedule. Find details for The Fillmore Miami Beach at Jackie Gleason Theater in Miami Beach, FL, including upgrades, seating chart, and day of show information.
data.text:
Coming to a show? Here's a few things to know before you go!

Doors Time

Doors generally open one hour before the show's scheduled start time.

Bag Policy

Bags up to 12 x 6 x 12 are allowed in the venue. All bags will be searched prior to entry. Bags that are not clear will be subject to additional search.

What items are not allowed inside the Fillmore Miami Beach Theater?

The following items are prohibited for all shows: any bags that are outside of our Clear Bag Policy, weapons, alcohol, drugs, selfie sticks, lawn chairs, laser pointers, skates, animals, wallet chains, spiked jewelry/belts, banners, backpacks, flyers, beach balls, Frisbees, fireworks, sparklers, video equipment laptops and tablets. Any item deemed dangerous by the venue General Manager or Law Officer. Recording equipment is prohibited at most shows, at the performer's discretion.

Mobile Ticketing

All our events will be Mobile Entry. That means your mobile device will be used to gain access to the event. Tickets will not be emailed or available for print.

For more information on mobile entry, click here.

Phone troubles? Visit the box office on event day for assistance. Be prepared to show your ID.

Cashless Payments

We are Cashless!
